- cs.SD (Sound) is a possible category as the paper deals with speech recognition and audio data. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with machine learning and natural language processing. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possible category as the paper deals with image classification and few-shot learning, which are related to computer vision.
